Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:27.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,第二话 成人式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好 拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:32.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,又看见了 拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:36.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不行啊\N我正更换感光玻璃板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:41.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,关掉收音机\N我不能集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:44.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是波斯托尼亚城堡吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这里是希尔索斯天文台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:50.33,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,知道 继续保持观测
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:52.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,阅兵仪式要赶快了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.12,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不请自来的客人终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:01:59.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:02.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,苏丝亚 恭喜你单独飞行成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:03.87,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不用奉承我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,除了飞行时间较短以外 你合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:08.47,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那边的不是更厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:14.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰对机械的感觉特别敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:17.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是我让他学驾驶飞机的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:19.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,苏丝亚你身为海姆家的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:20.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,却想成为市民军的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:22.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真的很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因为我有个父亲是飞机制造商的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,家里的事就拜托姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果让我做官员或商人的夫人那就抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你真奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:39.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民军的阅兵仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,要在夏至的前一日举行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:41.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:43.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那不是成人式开始的日子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:45.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,所以 很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.31,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不能去参观\N你们两人的成人式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我要驾驶这架飞机参加阅兵仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:54.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因为你爸爸的设计被采用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:57.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好 装好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.42,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,可是 莱因福特老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不让我的工场生产全部的飞机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.97,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,一半以上在他自己的工场里生产
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:10.69,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 为了量产的设备 要投资很多钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我家从爷爷那一代便开始制造飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:18.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,现在就是得到回报的时候\N也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:21.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,感谢战争这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.38,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果在海战上出动飞机进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:25.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,加利亚的领主\N会被吓得脸色发青啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.11,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,注意那边的机枪\N你们怎么搞的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:31.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,为什么阅兵仪式要在那一天举行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果在成人节之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我也就能以市民军一员的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,参加阅兵仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,讨厌！座位很热！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你坐在后面就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰你不觉得热吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:43.23,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我是司机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:47.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你真的打算加入市民军吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.47,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:51.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你也是啊 罗兰\N加入市民军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:54.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我由老爷来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.32,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,美雪你也说两句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:59.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,苏丝亚\N你得到爸爸的批准了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:02.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我自己的事由我自己来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,成人节要努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:06.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,阅兵仪式 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:07.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:29.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,今天是我的成人式！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:45.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:46.91,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好痛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你这个孩子真怕痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好痛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,露宿山头跌伤 真蠢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,今日非常忙的 赶快换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:57.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:04.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是市民军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,全部都会参加诺克斯市的阅兵仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,扩音机和探射灯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.83,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,看着前面嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:17.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,靠右行驶 右面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,很大规模啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:27.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,比想象中盛大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民军的阅兵仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:32.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在域辛镇的成人式那天举行\N这样好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:35.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,公子也有很多事情要考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.69,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,为什么这里靠近大街却很静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:41.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因为这里也用作员工宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:43.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,可是 不觉得太大吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.11,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你们很早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,尺寸是一个月前量的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,连一毫米都不会差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是不是瘦了些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:01.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,越来越像迪安娜陛下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,能参加波斯托尼亚城堡的派对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我很羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:07.42,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你后年也会被邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,而且 今天是成人式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大学那边如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,还未开学我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,反正只会教些我已知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.52,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我想投身社会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.12,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这孩子在胡说些什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,爸爸你可以帮我问一问吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,想在城堡的\N行政府里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.47,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这里的墙壁需要些画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,要是兼职\N多少我都能帮你找到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.47,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我想就业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.54,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:35.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不要再谈那话题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,阅兵仪式要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,三时一定要去到诺克斯市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你记得游园会的地点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:43.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:46.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,哦?罗兰不一起去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:48.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因为司机不可以坐在贵宾席
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:49.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你去见诺克斯市的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我没那打算…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不要紧啊\N因为今日是特别的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:22.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,向英格历撤领主\N莱因福特大人敬礼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真的威风凛凛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:33.27,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,加利亚真的会横渡大西洋进攻这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,就是为了预防他们进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:38.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,才需要这种有组织的军队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:40.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你真的打算加入市民军吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:43.91,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,跟你不想上大学\N想投身社会一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:45.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,仪态很差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:51.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民军加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:54.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民军的飞机部队来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:58.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,居于地球的人\N为何总是向上望而不向下望?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因为他们不想离开地面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:04.29,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果回归开始了\N你们有什么打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不想作为回归者登记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我也会继续学习弄面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我要让大家吃到美味的面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我会成为这里的报社记者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.11,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:16.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,经过今日的成人节
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我便会成为域辛镇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,飞机部队呀！数量很多！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:26.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,美雪在其中一部飞机上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是航空部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:33.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那个该不会跟迪安娜回归军战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.21,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是用来防护加利亚的飞艇的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:40.15,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下会最先到达地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜·索雷尔会最后才降落地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:46.57,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,域辛镇的成人式是怎么样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不知道啊\N是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.33,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 有神秘感才好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,或许是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,恩?  礼炮吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:16.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不到加纳坦避暑吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,请阁下也多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:21.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我会考虑 请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:30.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你在找海姆先生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:33.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,帮我去找狄兰·海姆先生\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.29,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,成人节结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.31,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你有兴趣\N在波斯托尼亚城堡工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:43.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那个…诺克斯市对我来说太现代化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.26,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,域辛镇比较适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:48.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那么 我想你帮西多工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:51.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,寻矿的工作 现在也需要技术员的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,西多先生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你认识他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:55.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:58.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是谈工作的\N你可以介绍给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.88,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,与其上大学学些无谓的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:05.91,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我宁愿投身社会实地学习
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:12.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,公子 请恕我和次女失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:13.79,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:17.83,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我和长女会出席晚上的派对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:20.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,请你们专心举行你们的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:24.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗拉 请你考虑一下帮西多工作的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:25.20,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:35.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,格威先生怎么称呼罗兰为罗拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他比较适合罗拉这个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.03,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗拉你会帮挖掘工西多先生工作吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:46.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不是叫罗拉 我叫罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:49.29,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,格威少爷不停叫你罗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.03,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这里和这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,总共有六处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,腰部以上的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.87,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这附近?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:02.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不要 好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:04.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,六处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,还会有人溺水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.59,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,通宵祭典就是整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:14.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在WHITE DOLL前\N随意玩乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:17.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,重要的是通宵祭典开始时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.32,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,进行的神圣刻印仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是…  神圣刻印…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.33,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,转身\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.33,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这里、这里、这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在这六处地方刻上圣痕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因为WHITE DOLL身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,有那形状的痣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:36.51,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那么 为什么会有那种痕迹?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:39.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,传说中是那样 没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:43.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那些圣痕\N是用手指按下去做成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:45.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,男人只需要知道这些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:50.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你只须要吸引女人的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:07.21,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,准备！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,出发了！抬起神轿！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好  去西盖尔山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.97,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,老婆也来这里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:42.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:43.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:47.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你说过你对新时代有兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但我也喜欢跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:52.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我会让你看看新时代的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,稍后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.69,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那么 我代表被选中的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.33,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在WHITE DOLL面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.77,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,进行神圣刻印仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,谁愿意跟我一起去?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那个汤姆\N真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:18.11,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,加油！不要输给捷克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.59,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,地球是个好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大家！快回来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰·塞亚克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这就是不用电线\N也能通讯的机器?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:41.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是月之民送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:44.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,有居住于月亮上的种族吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:48.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,由于他们想移居地球\N所以我们增强了市民军来应对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:51.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,有那么多人涌来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不仅是英格历撤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.88,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他们还要求我们将\N北阿米利亚大陆的SUNBELT地带交给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:14:00.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这就是居住在月球的宇宙人的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.32,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,原来你一直那么辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.57,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在哪里！?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民军有报告吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是   正在询问各部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:30.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,有报告吗！?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:31.95,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民军的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,没理由能在夜间飞行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:43.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你也不是市民军的正式成员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:47.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,爸爸你造的轰炸机HIPHEAVY\N我也驾驶了很长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你有什么想法?  西多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在飞机在天空飞行的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,还举行这种仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,世间的事物非全部讲逻辑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:02.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,没什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,多亏了这仪式\N山上一个人也没有 正适合调查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:15.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,没问题吧  罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.42,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我…我不清楚   怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰你也转身脱掉衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:30.27,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,请赐我六个圣痕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:31.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,圣痕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我刚才交了给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:36.38,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:39.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我害羞得快要死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,讨厌   今日是成人节
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:47.52,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你还带着那种玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:50.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是吗?  因为今晚是最后一晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:56.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这…这是什么！?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.30,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是水蛭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,用它们在背部刻上圣痕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:00.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,出来了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,盖子可以扔掉 快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.27,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我自己会处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:06.69,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,出来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是水蛭\N从以前起就是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,水蛭?\N不需要很着急的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不这样做便不能成为大人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:17.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你已经迟了两年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:22.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你知道位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:23.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:25.26,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你在做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,WHITE DOLL在看着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,能否像个男子汉般\N完成通宵祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:33.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你是否被承认为成人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.31,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,又走出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:48.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什么声音！?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.95,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,诺克斯市的方向明亮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是火的颜色啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:52.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真的！起火啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:55.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,喂 罗兰！知道是哪里吗！?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:57.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,肯定是诺克斯市
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,火很大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:01.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好像整个城市在起火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什么?  探射灯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:08.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是轰炸吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:22.02,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什么?\N这帮家伙认真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,宾湛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.97,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,宾湛你回去镇压诺克斯市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:31.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我去西面戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 市民军出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:36.17,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民军的战斗力根本不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那么你回去 是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是什么！?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:17:59.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,认真的吗！?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,它在跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 它好像机械啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,BULWAN开火了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:11.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,野蛮人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:13.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,别胡闹了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:30.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什么！?  还是下山比较好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:35.23,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是舰队战级的长距离激光炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:38.03,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在迪安娜回归军的训练里见过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰  我们要继续通宵仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:50.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什么事！?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,罗兰！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,苏丝亚和罗兰被埋起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,什么东西? 发生什么事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:24.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,WHITE DOLL竟然粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:28.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是什么！?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是驾驶舱！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:34.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,它在动 有东西在发光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:36.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.29,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,驾驶舱是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:42.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,就是驾驶的座位 你不觉得很像么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:44.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那是座位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我下去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你说这种东西会动吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这是WHITE DOLL啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 那非常的亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你不觉得它好像会动吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,绝对是驾驶舱\N这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:58.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:19:59.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,苏丝亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,头部刚才好像动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这里比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:04.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,请你下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:07.02,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这东西靠什么开动的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,连头盔也有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但控制台很不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:20.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:21.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,随便碰它一下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:22.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:23.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:36.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,看起来像手臂的东西在动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:37.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,激光枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:47.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,WHITE DOLL里有个机械木偶吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.20,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:52.03,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,这是机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:54.30,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,机动战士为什么会变的像遗迹似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:57.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,苏丝亚！蹲下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:06.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,机动战士的反应！?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,地球应该没有机动战士的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:12.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,开枪了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市内被击中！为什么！?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:22.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,它自己在动 停不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,停下来！\N怎样停下来?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:31.26,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,中枪了！?  损毁情况如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,下次将直接命中我吗！?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我们迪安娜回归军的情报\N怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:05.30,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,停了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:09.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是\N驾驶舱的光并没有完全消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:11.01,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那么会动吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:12.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我看能够开动它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:14.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,起火啊！到处火光熊熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:15.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,哪里起火！?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:33.60,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁微热还未减退\N微熱がさめないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:40.91,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低头少年的瞳孔\Nうつむく少年の瞳は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:46.38,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝望心海\N心の海みつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:50.44,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静静地在微笑\静かにほほえんてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:56.89,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生 消逝\N生まれくるもの　消えてゆくもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:23:03.33,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宿命钟摆的两端\Nすべては宿命の振子の幅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:09.07,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过挫折的黑暗射进来\N挫折の闇を突き拔けみえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:14.48,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是真正的光明\Nそれが光の真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:17.10,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AURA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:25.21,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着黎明献给被遗忘的星球\N夜明けとともに忘れ去られる星に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:27.82,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AURA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:35.09,comment #9,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高的爱在那双细小的手里\N至上の愛は小さなその手の中にある
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:42.23,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不想姬艾尔和苏丝亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:44.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,被卷入战火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:47.51,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是 诺克斯市好像损毁严重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:49.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,身在大屋的老爷也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:51.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,虽然基斯想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.38,0:23:54.91,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我却坐上WHITE DOLL
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:57.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,虽然没有精神准备
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,次回 TURN A高达
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:02.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,节日之后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.69,0:24:05.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,战争之风刮起了
